# Architecture Rules

## 1. Layered architecture

```
UI (.razor, Controllers)   — inject interfaces only
    ↓
Service Layer (Infrastructure/Services/)
    ↓
Feature Layer (Infrastructure/Features/)   — EF Core extension methods, do not rewrite
    ↓
Database
```

`.razor` and controllers must **never** inject `ITenantDbContextFactory` or `IMapper` directly. All DB work via Service layer.

```razor
// Wrong
@inject ITenantDbContextFactory Factory
using var db = Factory.CreateDbContext();

// Correct
@inject IUserService UserService
_users = await UserService.GetAllUsersAsync(ct);
```

## 2. Service pattern for new module `[Module]`

1. **Interface** `Interfaces/I[Module]Service.cs` — GetAll/GetById/Create/Update/Delete signatures
2. **Implementation** `Services/[Module]Service.cs` — injects `ITenantDbContextFactory` + `IMapper`, delegates to Feature extension methods (`db.[Module]s.GetAllAsync(_mapper, ct)`)
3. **DI** `DependencyInjection.cs` — `services.AddScoped<I[Module]Service, [Module]Service>();`
4. **Controller/Razor** — inject `I[Module]Service`, remove direct db/mapper usage

## 3. Feature layer — do not rewrite

`Infrastructure/Features/` — static extension method classes on `TenantDbContext`. Never move or rewrite them. Services are thin wrappers only.

## 4. Enums → `StudioB2B.Domain/Constants/`, name ends with `Enum`

```
// Wrong: public enum OrderState  (any folder)
// Correct: StudioB2B.Domain/Constants/OrderStateEnum.cs → public enum OrderStateEnum
```

## 5. Options → `StudioB2B.Domain/Options/`, name ends with `Options`

```
// Wrong: public class JwtConfig
// Correct: StudioB2B.Domain/Options/JwtOptions.cs → public class JwtOptions
```

## 6. Tests — required for every new feature

| Scope | Project |
|---|---|
| Pure logic / services | `StudioB2B.Tests.Unit` |
| EF Core / CRUD | `StudioB2B.Tests.Integration` |
| Architecture rules | `StudioB2B.Tests.Unit/Architecture` |

**Unit:** xUnit + FluentAssertions, real objects (no mocking), name `Method_Scenario_ExpectedResult`.

```csharp
public class MyServiceTests
{
    private readonly MyService _sut = new();

    [Fact]
    public void Method_Scenario_ExpectedResult()
    {
        var result = _sut.Method(input);
        result.Should().Be(expected);
    }
}
```

**Integration:** `[Collection("Database")]` + `IClassFixture<TenantDbContextFixture>`, `ctx.SuppressAudit = true`, `DatabaseSeeder` helpers.

```csharp
[Collection("Database")]
public class MyEntityCrudTests : IClassFixture<TenantDbContextFixture>
{
    private readonly TenantDbContextFixture _fixture;
    public MyEntityCrudTests(TenantDbContextFixture fixture) => _fixture = fixture;

    [Fact]
    public async Task CreateEntity_Persists()
    {
        await using var ctx = _fixture.CreateContext();
        ctx.SuppressAudit = true;
        var entity = DatabaseSeeder.MyEntity();
        await ctx.CreateMyEntityAsync(entity);
        var loaded = await ctx.MyEntities.AsNoTracking().FirstOrDefaultAsync(e => e.Id == entity.Id);
        loaded.Should().NotBeNull();
        loaded!.Name.Should().Be(entity.Name);
    }
}
```

- Cover Create, Update, SoftDelete/Delete, at least one query/filter per Feature file
- `.AsNoTracking()` on reads; `.IgnoreQueryFilters()` only for soft-delete/system-row tests

**Architecture:** NetArchTest `[Fact]` in `ArchitectureTests.cs`.

**Checklist:**
- [ ] Unit tests for service/logic
- [ ] Integration tests for all Feature CRUD/query methods
- [ ] New enum → `EnumDescriptionTests`, `FunctionEnumMapTests`, `PageColumnEnumMapTests` auto-pick it up
